","1 tsp lemon juice"]}],"id":"r123514","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-KmCzLPlvvo0\/XZVQrVhlC_I\/AAAAAAAAdEU\/HM0zh0zrWHMGxzHlirYaN10qttz63zIbQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_UkIlIwjv1SfExKrV.png","title":"Pasta Salad with Cod and Tartare Sauce","publishedAt":"2016-08-15T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"34.1 g","fat":"39.8 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"73.8 g","calories":"3303 kJ \/ 790 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving bowl, jug, refrigerator","basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 45m","4 portions"]}